<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>com.bolwarratechnologies.this_note</id>

  <name>This Note</name>
  <summary>Private, offline-only notes with encryption</summary>

  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>LicenseRef-proprietary</project_license>

  <developer id="com.bolwarratechnologies">
    <name>Bolwarra Technologies</name>
  </developer>

  <description>
    <p>
      This Note is a private, offline-only note-taking app. Your notes never leave your
      device — no account, no cloud sync, no network access of any kind.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>AES-256-GCM encryption with per-note password protection</li>
      <li>Organize with nested folders, tags, and note-to-note links</li>
      <li>Mind-map your ideas visually with the built-in Synapse canvas</li>
      <li>Writing stats: word count, reading time, and tracked writing time</li>
      <li>12 themes, rich text formatting, and a clean three-panel layout</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      The master encryption key is stored in the OS secret service (GNOME Keyring /
      libsecret). No data is written outside your local app directory.
    </p>
  </description>

